</li>
<li class="ref">
<div id="bib33" class="citation"><span class="label">33.</span> <span class="mixed-citation" data-jats-publication-type="other"><span class="person-group" data-jats-person-group-type="author"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Sun</span>, <span class="given-names">L.</span></span> and <span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Lyu</span>, <span class="given-names">L.</span></span> </span><span class="article-title">Federated model distillation with noise-free differential privacy</span>. In <span class="source"><em>Proceedings of IJCAI</em> </span> (<span class="year">2021</span>), <span class="fpage">1563</span>–<span class="lpage">1570</span>.</span></div>
</li>
<li class="ref">
